---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Leter DMCA notice and takedown process." />
    <title>DMCA | leter.net</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-surface">
      <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-text">‚Üê Back to home</a>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-text">DMCA Notice</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-muted">
          <p>
            Copyright complaints related to material under leter.net control may be submitted for
            review by the domain administrator.
          </p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">1. What to include in a notice</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Include your contact information, identification of the copyrighted work, exact
              location of the allegedly infringing material, and a good-faith statement under
              penalty of perjury.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">2. DMCA contact</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              DMCA notices and copyright legal correspondence:
              <span class="text-text">abuse@leter.net</span>
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">3. Counter notice</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              If you believe a takedown was made in error, you may submit a valid counter notice for
              review under applicable law.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">4. Non-copyright abuse</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              For phishing, spam, fraud, impersonation, or other non-copyright abuse, use
              <span class="text-text">abuse@leter.net</span> and the
              <a class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2" href="/abuse">
                abuse reporting page
              </a>.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
